# Roborazzi 
# Golden screenshots are typically saved in `build/outputs/roborazzi` or `src/test/roborazzi`.
# We want to ignore the intermediate test output, but since `/build/` is already ignored above,
# if you later configure Roborazzi to save "golden" (reference) images to be committed, 
# you should place them in a non-ignored directory like `app/src/test/snapshots/`.
